                        <interp inst="t18500819-1407-verdict-1" type="verdictSubcategory" value="no_subcategory"></interp>GUILTY</rs>
                  </hi>* <hi rend="italic">of stealing the pillow-cases.</hi>—Aged 20.—<hi rend="italic">
                     <rs id="t18500819-1407-punishment-39" type="punishmentDescription">
